================================
 Chromium OS build environments
================================

These are a collection of environments used to successfully build Chromium OS

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

  auto.sh
    (For autobuild and autosync)

  host.sh
    Host machine environment.

  chroot.sh
    Chroot build environment.

  crypt.sh
    This environment is for the crypt_mount script.
    For more information about crypt_mount, see crypt_mount --help.
    (This may not be needed)

  server.sh
    This is used by the dev_server command for ota updates, etc.
    For more information about dev_server, see dev_server --help.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

To automatically source environments:

 On the host machine:
   Copy: host.profile to ~/.profile
   
   Or run:
     setup/host_environment.sh

 Inside the chroot:
   Copy chroot.bashrc to ~/.bashrc

   Or run:
     setup/chroot_environment.sh

